# Customer Churn Prediction & Analytics Dashboard
# Supply-Chain-Disruption-Simulator-Butterfly-Effect-
##  Project Overview

Customer churn is one of the most critical business challenges in subscription-based industries such as telecommunications, SaaS, banking, and insurance. Acquiring a new customer is often more expensive than retaining an existing one, making churn prediction a key business priority.

This project combines **Business Intelligence**, **Machine Learning**, and **Interactive Visualization** to help organizations identify customers at risk of leaving and understand the factors driving churn.

The solution consists of:

* 📈 Interactive Customer Churn Analytics Dashboard
* 🤖 Machine Learning-Based Churn Prediction Model
* 🌐 Streamlit Web Application
* 📊 Business Insights and Retention Recommendations

---

# 🎯 Business Problem

The company wants to understand:

### WHO is churning?

Identify customer segments with the highest churn rates.

### WHEN are customers churning?

Determine the stage in the customer lifecycle where churn is most likely.

### WHY are customers churning?

Discover the key drivers and behaviors associated with customer attrition.

### WHAT can be done to reduce churn?

Provide actionable recommendations to improve customer retention.

---

# 📂 Dataset

The dataset contains customer demographic, service usage, contract, billing, and churn information.

### Key Features

| Feature          | Description                        |
| ---------------- | ---------------------------------- |
| Customer ID      | Unique customer identifier         |
| Age              | Customer age                       |
| Gender           | Male/Female                        |
| Tenure           | Number of months with company      |
| Monthly Charges  | Monthly subscription charges       |
| Total Charges    | Total amount paid                  |
| Contract Type    | Month-to-month, One Year, Two Year |
| Payment Method   | Customer payment method            |
| Tech Support     | Availability of technical support  |
| Online Security  | Security service subscription      |
| Churn            | Target variable (Yes/No)           |

