# 📊 Key Business Insights

The analysis revealed:

* Customers on month-to-month contracts churn significantly more than customers with long-term contracts.
* Customers with high monthly charges have higher churn probability.
* Most churn occurs during the early stages of the customer lifecycle.
* Lack of technical support and online security services increases churn risk.
* Early customer engagement is critical for retention.

